law.text:
In addition to any powers and duties set forth elsewhere by the laws of the State, the Commissioner:
has the powers and authority expressly conferred on the Commissioner by or reasonably implied from this article;
shall enforce this article;
shall perform the duties imposed on the Commissioner by this article; and
in addition to examinations and investigations expressly authorized, may conduct examinations and investigations of insurance matters as necessary to fulfill the purposes of this article.
